Places of interest in Valencia

Valencia_POIS.Rd

Geospatial references for places of interest in Valencia

Usage

data(Valencia_POIS)

Valencia_POIS

Format

A list with three objects:

City_Center

Coordinates of Valencia's city center

Metro

Coordinates of Valencia's metro

Blasco

Coordinates of Blasco Avenue)

An object of class list of length 3.

Source

Idealista (https://www.idealista.com/)

Examples

 library(idealista18)
 data(Valencia_POIS)
 summary(Valencia_POIS)
#>             Length Class      Mode
#> City_Center 2      data.frame list
#> Metro       2      data.frame list
#> Blasco      2      data.frame list
